These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, martial-arts, zombie
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, tiparillo, bongani
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, d&b, dubstep
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, august, april
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, water-polo, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the bongani-smoker##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the tiparillo-smoker is the person watching zombie movies##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the fan of country##1
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | soy-milk   | 7up           |
| Movie-Genre          | martial-arts       | zombie    | family         |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking        |
| Cigar           | havana | tiparillo   | bongani      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | dubstep    | country       |
| Birthday   | august     | december  | april       |
| Sport         | tennis     | water-polo | weightlifting |

