The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, september, january
3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, mouse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, swimming
 1. the person drinking almond-milk is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person traveling to hannover is the person drinking tea##1
 4. the person traveling to boston is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's birthday is in september and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
11. the person who's birthday is in september is the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Beverage          | tea      | almond-milk      | coffee      |
