 3. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
 4. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of country##1
 5. the fan of country is between the person who likes black and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the fan of country is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is the person who growsbellflower##1
 9. the person drinking milk is between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the boat##2
10. the malaysian is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
