3 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, go
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, documentary
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, july, april
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, guinea-pig
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, soccer, water-polo
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, blend, vegafina
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is in the middle##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 4. the person playing go is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the vegafina-smoker is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's birthday is in september##2
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is the bongani-smoker##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the bongani-smoker is the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | tea      |
| Game         | mah-jongg     | billiard     | go  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure  | disaster |
| Birthday   | july  | april     | september |
| Pet           | bird        | guinea-pig | fish     |
| Sport         | handball    | water-polo | soccer   |
| Cigar     | blend        | vegafina        | bongani   |

