.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, milk
House: townhouse, colonial, ranch-style
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, hiking, singing
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, manager, musician
3 different pets are kept: hamster, turtle, pony
3 different games are played: domino, bridge, canasta
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, ship, skateboard
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the musician##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
3. the colonial house is on the left of the dressmaker##1
4. the person playing domino is between the owner of the hamster and the manager##2
5. the ranch-style house is between the musician and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
7. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
9. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | fanta      | juice      | milk       |
| House          | colonial      | ranch-style    | townhouse   |
| Hobby         | singing    | baking     | hiking     |
| Job           | manager    | dressmaker | musician   |
| Pet   | turtle    | pony    | hamster       |
| Game         | canasta | domino      | bridge    |
| Transport     | ship       | helicopter | skateboard |

