.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: ivory, brown, ebony
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, peach, zucchini
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, photography, reading
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, scientific, superhero
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, jazz, reggae
House: futuristic, craftsman, cottage
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, egyptian, canadian
1. the egyptian is the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the craftsman house is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the cottage house is on the right of the craftsman house##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the canadian##1
5. the person eating peach is between the person who likes ebony and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
6. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
7. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
8. the turkish is the person watching superhero movies##1
9. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| Color      | ebony       | ivory     | brown         |
| Food          | lettuce     | peach      | zucchini     |
| Hobby         | photography | reading    | cooking      |
| Movie-Genre   | animation   | scientific | superhero    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz        | reggae     | electronic   |
| House         | futuristic     | craftsman | cottage |
| Nationality     | egyptian     | canadian       | turkish    |

