.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, tea
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, spinach, zucchini
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, fisherman, nurse
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, french, italian
3 different games are played: domino, go, canasta
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, mauve, coral
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, fonseca, chaman
1. the person drinking milk is the person eating zucchini##1
2. the chaman-smoker is the person who likes azure##1
3. the dressmaker is between the person drinking tea and the person playing canasta##2
4. the canadian is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
5. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
6. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
7. the fisherman is the person eating broccoli##1
8. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing domino##1
9. the french is between the person eating broccoli and the bluemaster-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | milk       | tea      |
| Food          | broccoli   | zucchini   | spinach  |
| Job           | fisherman  | dressmaker | nurse    |
| Nationality   | canadian   | french     | italian  |
| Game           | canasta     | domino        | go |
| Color         | mauve | azure   | coral  |
| Cigar     | fonseca    | chaman     | bluemaster      |

 